HEADWORD: off the hook
<hw>off` the hook"</hw> <pr>(⟦ocr⟧f` ⟦th⟧⟦ucr⟧ h⟦oocr⟧k")</pr>,
<pos>pred. adj.</pos> <def>No longer considered responsible; <as>as,
